<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871211-0152 </DOCNO><HL> Bausch andamp; Lomb Completes Sale</HL><DD> 12/11/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> BOL CAMBYTENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><DATELINE> ROCHESTER, N.Y.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Bausch andamp; Lomb Inc. said it completed the sale of three business lines -- its microscope, photogrammetry and diagnostic ophthalmic instruments operations -- to Cambridge Instrument PLC, of Cambridge, England, for $37 million. </TEXT></DOC>